{"tid":529754,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇D實用既管理技巧？","createTime":"2018-01-15T05:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T01:18:39.000Z","uid":20747,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"55e7baea6a10738a86c5c6999292d1d9e7f8fdff","tid":529754,"uid":20747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"最近升左做管理層<br />\n係做Sales既<br />\n團隊裡面有十個人左右<br />\n以80 90 後為主<br />\n<br />\n以我既概念：隻狗鐘意食咩就比咩佢食，之後隻狗要達到你要求先再比佢食，同埋做人要有條介線話比佢聽，邊個接觸你既底線都係死路一條<br />\n<br />\n想問各位巴打絲打有咩實用既管理技巧可以分享下？"},{"pid":"1a5d235077ae681cb303cc0620bef4c8c6140381","tid":529754,"uid":97465,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"而定狗都做到管理層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a313b1acbf00c46751cd3816f3798f1fb18c438","tid":529754,"uid":20747,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"其實對D下屬係狗有咩問題？<br />\n最緊要比佢感覺到你對佢係人當佢係兄弟、朋友咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n你一對D下屬產生感情果陣，佢地一爆D咩獲或者當佢地冇曬生產力果陣就好難忍心搵佢地開刀，到時最尾只會搞死自己。"},{"pid":"52c0bd58fd2370e77482ac1b869f9262e2aa0a02","tid":529754,"uid":20747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T11:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b7730ad1971fd0407b738bba235cf9a7fd0848","tid":529754,"uid":53660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T11:29:18.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n<br />\n加人工<br />\n<br />\n夠唔夠實用？"},{"pid":"86089b8ece717213b654bed0ee3222a405f10dd7","tid":529754,"uid":20747,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n<br />\n加人工<br />\n<br />\n夠唔夠實用？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加人工都算管理技巧既一種⋯<br />\n但係有咩唔掂淨係加人工咁樣好低層次<br />\n<br />\n即係一同條女嘈交要哄返佢果陣就送名牌袋，旅行之類咁"},{"pid":"5dd0e4928a9b3ed1135b0b5e7d69725f4d50270b","tid":529754,"uid":14348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:54:12.000Z","msg":"一啖砂糖一